T-Shirt Offer

SunRize Industries now has its own T-shirt!  These handsome orange-and-black shirts are printed on front and back with our logo and product list.  Each shirt is 100% cotton machine washable fabric and comes in Large, X-Large, and XX-Large sizes.

Best of all, when you order any SI product directly from us, you can request one FREE!  These T-shirts are also sold seperately for $10.00.

 